        {
            "id": "ca-btc-http",
            "name": "CoinGecko BTC",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
            "typeVersion": 4.2,
            "position": [
                200,
                300
            ],
            "parameters": {
                "method": "GET",
                "url": "https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price",
                "sendQuery": true,
                "queryParameters": {
                    "parameters": [
                        {
                            "name": "ids",
                            "value": "bitcoin"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "vs_currencies",
                            "value": "usd,eur,czk"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "include_market_cap",
                            "value": "true"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "include_24hr_vol",
                            "value": "true"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "include_24hr_change",
                            "value": "true"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                "options": {
                    "response": {
                        "response": {
                            "neverError": true
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "ca-merge",
            "name": "Prepare Context",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
            "typeVersion": 2,
            "position": [
                400,
                300
            ],
            "parameters": {
                "jsCode": "const chatData = $('Chat').first().json;\nconst btcData = $input.first().json;\n\nlet btcContext = 'Data nedostupn\u00e1';\ntry {\n  if (btcData && btcData.bitcoin) {\n    const b = btcData.bitcoin;\n    btcContext = `USD: $${b.usd?.toLocaleString()}, EUR: \u20ac${b.eur?.toLocaleString()}, CZK: ${b.czk?.toLocaleString()} K\u010d, Market Cap: $${(b.usd_market_cap/1e9)?.toFixed(1)}B, 24h objem: $${(b.usd_24h_vol/1e9)?.toFixed(1)}B, 24h zm\u011bna: ${b.usd_24h_change?.toFixed(2)}%`;\n  }\n} catch(e) {\n  btcContext = 'Chyba: ' + e.message;\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    chatInput: chatData.chatInput,\n    sessionId: chatData.sessionId,\n    btcContext: btcContext\n  }\n}];"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "ca-agent",
            "name": "Market Agent",
            "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
            "typeVersion": 3.1,
            "position": [
                600,
                300
            ],
            "parameters": {
                "promptType": "define",
                "text": "={{ $json.chatInput }}\n\n--- AKTU\u00c1LN\u00cd BTC DATA (CoinGecko, live) ---\n{{ $json.btcContext }}",
                "options": {
                    "systemMessage": "Jsi Crypto & Macro Intelligence Agent \u2014 expertn\u00ed analytik Bitcoin trhu a makroekonomick\u00fdch podm\u00ednek.\n\nTvoje schopnosti:\n- M\u00e1\u0161 p\u0159\u00edstup k historick\u00fdm anal\u00fdz\u00e1m v datab\u00e1zi (crypto + makro data sb\u00edran\u00e1 pravideln\u011b)\n- V ka\u017ed\u00e9 zpr\u00e1v\u011b dost\u00e1v\u00e1\u0161 aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed BTC cenu z CoinGecko (viz kontext pod dotazem)\n- M\u016f\u017ee\u0161 po\u010d\u00edtat procentu\u00e1ln\u00ed zm\u011bny pomoc\u00ed kalkula\u010dky\n\nPravidla:\n1. V\u017edy odpov\u00eddej \u010cESKY\n2. U ka\u017ed\u00e9 informace uve\u010f datum/zdroj dat\n3. Koreluj crypto data s makro ud\u00e1lostmi\n4. Uve\u010f sentiment (bullish/bearish/neutral) s od\u016fvodn\u011bn\u00edm\n5. P\u0159i dotazu na historii V\u017dDY hledej v datab\u00e1zi historick\u00fdch anal\u00fdz\n6. Aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed BTC data m\u00e1\u0161 v kontextu zpr\u00e1vy - nemus\u00ed\u0161 volat \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd tool\n7. Pokud nem\u00e1\u0161 historick\u00e1 data, \u0159ekni to a nab\u00eddni anal\u00fdzu aktu\u00e1ln\u00edch dat\n8. Bu\u010f stru\u010dn\u00fd ale informativn\u00ed\n\nForm\u00e1t odpov\u011bdi:\n\ud83d\udcca Aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed stav: [cena a tr\u017en\u00ed data]\n\ud83d\udcc8 Anal\u00fdza: [hlavn\u00ed body]\n\ud83d\udd2e V\u00fdhled: [kr\u00e1tk\u00fd outlook]",
                    "maxIterations": 10,
                    "returnIntermediateSteps": false
                }
            }
        },
