            "parameters": {
                "name": "calculator",
                "description": "Kalkula\u010dka pro v\u00fdpo\u010dty procentu\u00e1ln\u00edch zm\u011bn, cenov\u00fdch rozd\u00edl\u016f a porovn\u00e1n\u00ed. Vstup je JavaScript matematick\u00fd v\u00fdraz jako string. P\u0159\u00edklad: '(85000 - 80000) / 80000 * 100' vr\u00e1t\u00ed procentu\u00e1ln\u00ed zm\u011bnu.",
                "code": "const expression = query;\ntry {\n  const result = new Function('return ' + expression)();\n  return JSON.stringify({ result: Number(result.toFixed(4)), expression });\n} catch (e) {\n  return JSON.stringify({ error: 'Neplatn\u00fd v\u00fdraz: ' + e.message });\n}"
            }
